About : the kind of login
SQL : level

0 - Shop Keeper
1 - Administrator
2 - Super Admin (do NOT give out!) [Not editable]


######################################################
______________________________________________________

######################################################

SQL : permission
About : Bitwise permissions of login

MSB ... LSB

00 - can view admin panel
01 - can view all customers (if false, can only edit those of shop) (fully remove edit by setting shopID to 0)
	Make sure view/retrieve and customer info is working!
02 - can add new customer (only to own shop ids - 01 allowed all shop IDs!)
03 - can edit current customers (only viewable ones!)
04 - can soft-delete and resture current customers
05 - can hard-delete current customers (removes from SQL) (do NOT give out!)
06 - can add login
07 - can edit login
08 - can edit admin
09 - can edit super admin
10 - can edit system settings


